

user_metrics puppet module for MediaWiki vagrant VM.

This uses the MediaWiki database set up by the MediaWiki
module to host a user_metrics dev instance.  See:
https://metrics.wikimedia.org for the production version.

Usage:

In your site.pp:

  class { 'user_metrics': }

Then run

  vagrant provision

That should set up a user_metrics flask web app running in
WSGI in apache.  It will be accessible at http://10.11.12.13:8121.

